{"tid":588252,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC] 7 Days to Die -- PVE喪屍生存","createTime":"2018-03-11T05:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T17:27:43.000Z","uid":47480,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"537b47581bcc77bac35db374b20990f28087bb09","tid":588252,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:35:09.000Z","msg":"7 Days to die 係一隻PVE喪屍生存遊戲，一開始玩家身上基乎乜都冇，由劈樹、挖石仔、執草黎合成基本工具起屋，或者大膽既可以去荒廢城鎮搜括物資 (有大量喪屍，隨時打開門幾隻衝上黎)，建立自己既據點抵擋喪屍既侵襲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/gfx5l7iGs4g/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fgfx5l7iGs4g%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=89ca9456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲系統十分寫實，有體溫系統，唔夠凍要著衫或者圍爐取溫，熱要除衫/飲水散熱/或者直接跳落水，新手黎講呢點都幾麻煩，因為太熱太凍會扣血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同行動緩慢。 <br />\n<br />\n遊戲大部份喪屍朝早4:00至夜晚22:00前係呆滯遊走狀態，唔識跑，唔識遠攻，基本上你見到跑走都可以。但一到夜晚22:00至04:00 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你點跑都唔夠佢快，所以每晚22:00最好搵定地方匿埋。仲有喪屍狗..喪屍熊...呢啲就唔介紹。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲每逢第7日為一個循環，嗰日叫做Bloodmoon，嗰日夜晚(22:00至04:00)，喪屍會持續係你身邊出現，殺一隻，SPWAN一隻，就算你匿喺邊，都會搵到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n遊戲入面仲有<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">電力系統</span></strong>，電燈/陷阱/炮台/電欄，個人最鍾意係刀片陷阱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UmF3Uy8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUmF3Uy8.jpg&h=4bb3bf1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/_ZKLaoU-vnE/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F_ZKLaoU-vnE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a8071d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pp.userapi.com/c837725/v837725103/68b5d/YMZ5XdzjDj8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpp.userapi.com%2Fc837725%2Fv837725103%2F68b5d%2FYMZ5XdzjDj8.jpg&h=0d64b2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前遊戲入面唯一交通工具 minibike ， 黎緊下一次更新會有新載具 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://apollo2.dl.playstation.net/cdn/EP2026/CUSA03455_00/FREE_CONTENT6pXAPwGcOtfntVD03wdq/7daytodie_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapollo2.dl.playstation.net%2Fcdn%2FEP2026%2FCUSA03455_00%2FFREE_CONTENT6pXAPwGcOtfntVD03wdq%2F7daytodie_02.jpg&h=5b23fdcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想入手既可以睇下下面條片先<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c4g7Dq_TqPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc4g7Dq_TqPQ&d=wnrB4YlbdlhvLVZtTTAyVDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b7d58baf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c4g7Dq_TqPQ</a><br />\n<br />\n入手網址 : <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/251570/7_Days_to_Die/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F251570%2F7_Days_to_Die%2F&d=wnrB4YlbdlhvLVZtTTAyVDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d5695cb5\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/251570/7_Days_to_Die/</a>"},{"pid":"91587be1285e8561f09baa7e7ec3e7277c326e18","tid":588252,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"樓主今日會開新server  有興趣可以一齊玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb14e5187336eccc9d5ca0391a8bf8a821cb9cde","tid":588252,"uid":136662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"話說依家咩版本<br />\n果時新出玩咗陣就無玩<br />\n仲記得話下個版本更新食人蜂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0f448189692969cf31f170984576ff47b7f805","tid":588252,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb14e5187336eccc9d5ca0391a8bf8a821cb9cde","tid":588252,"uid":136662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"話說依家咩版本<br />\n果時新出玩咗陣就無玩<br />\n仲記得話下個版本更新食人蜂<img s